reviewText: I wanted to see duet's. There were none. If you get a DVD with duet's from this couple let me know.

would've thought this was a dvd of Tammy & George singing together....not
but it was ok....would like to find a dvd of their duets.

The dvd by George Jones and Tammy Wynette was fine. Just wish that there were more songs on the tape with both of them singin together. It is a older tape and I just like to see them sing together because they sound so perfect. Recommend anyone to buy it who loves to hear George and Tammy sing.
Disappointed. Not enough George & Tammy. Won't push for people to buy it. Actually it is a "one' on the "Like" scale.
